      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EYE CAN EAR AMOUR (4) enjoyed the class drop from the city when he dug deep to score last week at Newcastle. That was in a higher-graded race than this and he should be able to push forward again from this barrier so looks tough to stop. Hard to knock the recent consistency of MAJOR AUSTIN (2) who added to a string of wins and placings when third last start at Newcastle. Led to score prior so can give a big sight from a low draw. WICKED WHISKEY (5) hasn't been too far away of late including a fourth after racing wide from this barrier two back at Menangle. Race fit now so could show his best. BELLAMYS BLAST (1) has come from the back row in each start this time in and showed improvement last time. Include from the ace draw.",
